 test purposes (
\begin_inset Formula $dP/dx$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $dP/dy$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $d^{2}P/dx^{2}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $d^{2}P/dy^{2}$
\end_inset

).
