\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $G_{r}=(n_{+}-n_{-})/(n_{+}+n_{-})$
\end_inset

.
 This corresponds to the values that can be calculated for a whole epoch
 in 
\series bold
avg_q
\series default
 by the method 
\series bold
calc_binomial_items
\series default
.
\end_layout

